<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="neighbour-n">neighbo(u)r <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'neɪbə(r)/    美 /'neɪbər/  </p>
<p>[C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>邻居；邻国；邻近的人 / 物：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>next-door neighbours 
隔壁邻居</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Israel and its neighbours 
以色列及其邻国</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A good neighbour is better than a brother far off. 
远亲不如近邻。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>One of our <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (邻居) kept a very beautiful garden.  （2008 全国）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. neighbo(u)rs  </p></div>